descriptionHtml:
Jennifer Lawrence NORD CME save slot.
To get her to look EXACTLY like she does in my images, you'll need the following mods:

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/? (IMPORTANT: MAKE SURE TO USE VERSION 0.85!)

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36925/? (download both the core AND morphs.)

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?

SG Hairs (268 edition) Google for it. It's worth the hassle!

(Also, if you ARE going to be using a large hair mod, use this: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?)


http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54814/? (Only use the normal maps (_msn.dss files) from the texture folder.)

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36425/?

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28946/?

After installing these files, download THIS mod and install/extract it to data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets


If there are ANY problems/concerns/needs of help, message me. I'm on my computer 24/7 ^~^


Enjoy!
author: Kaiskaahpa
